---
title: Chorizo and Prawn Tacos with harissa aioli and spicy wedges
description: The best types of tacos are those where you have a myriad of flavours and textures in every bite. That's exactly what you'll experience when you taste the spicy, herby, meaty tongue-tingling filling in these tortillas.
